.title Help: Base System Package
ABOUT THIS PACKAGE
The Base System package is the foundation for all your
other packages.  It is required for all installations
and provides support for most binary applications.
This package includes:

  --  Intel Application Binary Interface compatibility
  --  Basic UNIX shell command interfaces
  --  Basic administrative capabilities
  --  Required hardware support
  --  Basic file system support

EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Install Menu.
                                    (CONTINUED)
.page
EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Package Selection menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
